INDEX.DESCRIPTION: This feature allows you to search for canvases, doodles and fields in the above search bars (one for each eye). Clicking on a search result will take you to the relevant item and if it is a doodle it will add it for you.
INDEX.GENERAL_NOTE:
Shortcuts:
Ctrl+Alt+R = Start search in right eye
Ctrl+Alt+L = Start search in left eye

INDEX.DESCRIPTION: Post operative refractive target in dioptres
The post operative refractive target has been discussed with the patient

Anterior chamber lens are fixed with the support of iris. Primarily used as a backup lens when there is damage to the Posterior Chamber. AC IOL is also used in refractive surgery – implanting a lens in phakic eye to correct the refractive power.
